Thanx for RPing IR for me, Yan.

* Iron Raptor snarled and began to climb up towards Menasors' shoulders, her 
claws going to slam down and dig deep into his armor plating while she let 
Prowl have a bit of the fun around his neck.
She stopped about mid way up, which would be the center of his back, 
thinking to herself that he couldn't possiby be able to reach with his arms 
to where she was unless he was super flexable.
Smiling to herself, Iron Raptor began to kneed, her claws digging and 
scratching while she lowered her head towards the center of his back with a 
BIG bite!
She moved to sink her teeth in, remembering that her very saliva was acid 
based and he'd feel that more then he would her teeth.*
